          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-1" n="1">(1)<lb/>Here Sarum lies, of late as Wise</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-2" n="2">And Learned as Aquinas,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-3" n="3">Lawn Sleeves he wore, yet was no more</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-4" n="4">A Christian, than Socinus.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-5" n="5">(2)<lb/>Oaths, pro &amp; con, he swallow'd down,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-6" n="6">Loved Gold like any lay-Man,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-7" n="7">Wrote, preach'd and pray'd, and yet betry'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-8" n="8">God's holy Church for Mammon.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-9" n="9">(3)<lb/>Of e'ery Vice, he had a spice,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-10" n="10">Altho' a Reverend Prelate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-11" n="11">Yet liv'd and dyed, if not bely'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-12" n="12">A true dissenting Zealot.</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-13" n="13">(4)<lb/>If such a Soul, to Heaven stole,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-14" n="14">And 'scap'd the Devil's clutches,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-15" n="15">We'll then presume, there may be room</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-058Y-line-16" n="16">For Marlboro' and his Dutches.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
